  N3 -->|Primary| N4{PB: Remote Functions - Generate single-source risk mitigation strategies using Remote Functions.}
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Model supply disruption scenarios using Cortex Auto Forecast.]
  N5 --> N6[UI: UI Screens - Surface actionable insights and recommendations via UI Screens.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital volatility, improved on-time delivery, and minimized COGS exposure.]
  N3 -->|High geopolitical risk detected.| B1[Trigger disaster recovery plan.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Preserve supply chain flow during geopolitical disruptions.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Single-source supplier identified as ...| B2[Implement alternative sourcing decisions.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Reduce dependency on single-source suppliers.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Supply disruption scenario indicates ...| B3[Adjust capacity and sourcing plans.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Enhance network resilience against potential disruptions.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]